{"tid":738871,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"原來譚伯老豆見過希特拉","createTime":"2018-07-11T20:31:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T22:51:59.000Z","uid":28765,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"70017f580443a7c077c9adb7b6e84f0ecbb66bf7","tid":738871,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T20:31:25.000Z","msg":"1934年5月，第十屆遠東運動會在菲律賓首都馬尼拉舉行，譚江柏有份入選中華民國足球隊，並且在決賽與球王李惠堂各入兩球，以4－3擊敗日本隊，完成九連霸[5]。<br />\n<br />\n1936年，代表中華民國前往德國的首都柏林參加奧運足球賽，獲當時納粹德國元首希特勒頒授過一隻懷錶。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934938eaa1d898353abac4079ae4d497a26d9aee","tid":738871,"uid":9681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T20:39:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917eeb9b668cc0c56a1585a61d10387b8746ff28","tid":738871,"uid":40662,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T21:11:34.000Z","msg":"譚伯都應該就快見到"},{"pid":"e0f380c8bcce8d34d1f68bd14bc149ec82bac8ea","tid":738871,"uid":137166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T21:24:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f42736e8b09cd7ab161b6160553b27b2de3011c","tid":738871,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"917eeb9b668cc0c56a1585a61d10387b8746ff28","tid":738871,"uid":40662,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T21:11:34.000Z","msg":"譚伯都應該就快見到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T21:59:41.000Z","msg":"我~~~追～～～趕"},{"pid":"2d59af302c1250dabaa83598bc016082550009ce","tid":738871,"uid":171720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"917eeb9b668cc0c56a1585a61d10387b8746ff28","tid":738871,"uid":40662,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T21:11:34.000Z","msg":"譚伯都應該就快見到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T22:51:59.000Z","msg":"屌 login 比正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 